{"id":"110367608340282718","created_at":"2023-05-14T14:54:15.001Z","in_reply_to_id":"110366992289097709","in_reply_to_account_id":"235099","sensitive":false,"spoiler_text":"","visibility":"public","language":"en","uri":"https://chaos.social/users/foosel/statuses/110367608340282718","url":"https://chaos.social/@foosel/110367608340282718","replies_count":2,"reblogs_count":8,"favourites_count":23,"quotes_count":0,"edited_at":null,"content":"\u003cp\u003eWith the latest update that adds some final polishing (and after making another run through to make sure everything looks ok), I\u0026#39;m calling a wrap on \u0026quot;Pew Pew Pew: Danger Zone!\u0026quot; and my first \u003ca href=\"https://chaos.social/tags/gamejam\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\"\u003e#\u003cspan\u003egamejam\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWow, what an experience. Woke up last Saturday to the theme, thought about it during my morning routine, came up with an idea \u0026amp; put down a plan that felt doable in the available time. And - to my absolute surprise - this plan worked out! Beyond proud! 😊\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://foosel.itch.io/pew-pew-pew-danger-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003efoosel.itch.io/pew-pew-pew-dan\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003eger-zone\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","reblog":null,"application":{"name":"Web","website":null},"account":{"id":"235099","username":"foosel","acct":"foosel","display_name":"Gina Häußge","locked":false,"bot":false,"discoverable":true,"indexable":true,"group":false,"created_at":"2020-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","note":"\u003cp\u003e🐒 Passionate code monkey 👩‍💻 Geek 🎮 Gamer 🧗‍♀️ Bouldering apprentice 💡 Problem solver 🐍 Python wrangler 🐙 Creator \u0026amp; Maintainer of OctoPrint\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdmin of plushies.social \u0026amp